import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground } from 'docz';
import Wrapper from './Wrapper';
import RcRangePicker from '../../src/RcRangePicker';

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"rcrangepicker"}}>{`RcRangePicker`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Date range picker.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Property`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Type`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`required`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`default`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`startDate`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Date, string`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`true`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`''`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`endDate`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Date, string`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`true`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`''`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`onSelectRange`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`function`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`true`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
